---
title: Brown Sugar-Glazed Salmon with Garlic Rice and Green Beans
description: The combo of roasted salmon and fluffy rice is always a hit and tonight the family will really love the sweet and savoury flavours that come with it. The salmon is glazed with a sauce made from brown sugar, soy sauce and hoisin sauce, and the rice is boosted with garlic. Green beans are the natural side to complete this ideal plate!
